20th (Old Bowery)Road, north side, between 41st (left) and 42nd Streets (right), showing old Steinway property. The house in the view is doubtfully referred to as the Theodore Steinway house by Eugene L. Armbruster, the collector. It does not appear in the E. Belcher Hyde Atlas of Queens
in 1928.
